      "content": "but it wasnt lightning. lightning doesn't come in three distinct, high-intensity bursts followed by a long pause, then two more. it was way too regular. and it happened right as the news was talking about the president's latest policy shift. it felt like a direct response. if you look at the timing and the rhythm, how can you just dismiss it as natural? there has to be a pattern here that links the timing to what's happening in dc right now.",
